{"tid":324385,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【商舖消息】先達地舖首錄撻定 買家輸定蝕80萬","createTime":"2017-07-16T11:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T17:10:44.000Z","uid":17738,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a581f445d5fde72d946e54eb7af782dfbeb42272","tid":324385,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170716/large/1500189812_1bfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170716%2Flarge%2F1500189812_1bfc.jpg&h=e2c0dc1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手機店林立的旺角先達廣場今年頻錄蝕讓成交，最近更罕有地錄得近年首次撻定個案。商場地下59號舖，建築面積130方呎，今年2月易手，成交價800萬元，惟上月底買家取消買賣合約，撻定損失80萬元。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，旺角先達廣場地下59號舖，今年2月以800萬元易手。文件顯示，買家已支付成交價10%作為定金，即約80萬元，惟6月底取消買賣合約。<br />\n<br />\n根據紀錄，該場今年至少3宗蝕讓成交，其中地下G100號舖位以533.8萬元易手，業主在iPhone熱炒年代入市，持貨七年慘輸334.2萬元，新買家是活躍舖市、人稱「太子鄧」的太子珠寶鐘錶主席鄧鉅明。追溯過去5年，該場未聞撻定個案，今次屬首宗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56962494&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56962494%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170716&d=ZgipvXiRYYR0mtyNn%2FpteQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=0b35192b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56962494%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170716&h=fea177ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56962494&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170716</a>"},{"pid":"a74b1b3667b04077f96f510f9432f63185818310","tid":324385,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:10:44.000Z","msg":"先達都撻?　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁買邊度先唔撻  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}